    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Educational institutions teaching at a level intermediate between elementary school and high school. The term is used primarily in North America, and usually covers grades 7 through 9. In some areas, usage with "middle schools" may overlap; however, most school systems that have a middle school typically do not also have a junior high school. Middle schools in most areas accept children a year or two younger than those in junior high schools.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000114707/Oxford English Dictionary Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>所提供之教育銜接小學和高中的教育機構。此詞彙主要於北美地區使用，通常指7到9年級。在部分地區可能和「中學」（middle schools）的意思重疊；但大部分有「中學」的學制裡通常不會再出現「初級中學」。在大多數的地區，中學新生比一般初級中學新生小1到2歲。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Onderwijsinstellingen in de Verenigde Staten die meestal de eerste drie klassen van de middelbare school omvatten. In sommige regio's komt de betekenis overeen met 'middle schools', maar de meeste schoolsystemen met een middle school kennen meestal geen junior high school. In de meeste regio's worden op middle schools kinderen toegelaten die een of twee jaar jonger zijn dan kinderen in junior high schools.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
